    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "あの友達と、どこで知り合ったのかって？",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "別に、普通だけど……SNSで繋がったとか\nよく行くバーでバイトしてた子に紹介されたとか",
      "startTime": 9.3666666348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "みんな忙しいし、あんまりしょっちゅうは遊べないけど\nって、なんであんたがkanaの友達気にしてる訳？",
      "startTime": 17.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "なんというか……いい人達ですね\n芸能人のkanaさんを、特別扱いする感じでもないし",
      "startTime": 26.1666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "困ってたら、ああやって手伝いに来てくれるし\n俺にも着替えを貸してくれましたし……",
      "startTime": 34.0666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう。いい人達なのよ\n……あー、あんたの言いたいことなんとなく分かった",
      "startTime": 41.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "いい人なのに、友達なのに\nなんで嘘くさい態度なんだ、とか言いたいんでしょ",
      "startTime": 50.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "前に言ったでしょ\n本当のことを言うだけが、正しい訳じゃないって",
      "startTime": 56.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "別に嘘でも、みんなで楽しい方がいいじゃん",
      "startTime": 60.8666668255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "……それに、いい人達と友達やれるなら\nkanaもいい人になれるかもって、自信つくから",
      "startTime": 69.6333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですか",
      "startTime": 74.8000006674,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ならfranさんとmihoさんは、友達じゃないけど\n言いたいことを言える相手ってことになるんですかね？",
      "startTime": 80.2333221434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "それさぁ、ほっこりした顔で言わないでくれる？\nすんげえムカつくから",
      "startTime": 87.3333221434,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8580.003051800006,
          "startTime": 95.9133251952
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8580.656433100003,
          "startTime": 95.9139785765
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_ball-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8566.669718500008,
          "startTime": 95.8999918619
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "あいつらとはプレタポルテに言われて組んだだけで\n目的達成したら、さっさと縁切りたいんだから",
      "startTime": 92.7666554767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "え……なんか今、凄い音がしたけど……\n何かプールに落っことしでもしたの？",
      "startTime": 100.7999852496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "……って、うわ、プールに落ちたのmihoかよ",
      "startTime": 103.5666622478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "あのまま放っておいたら、女神が出てきて\n金のmihoか銀のmihoと交換してくれないかなぁ",
      "startTime": 111.6666534422,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9733.331298799996,
          "startTime": 121.399984741
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "童話の斧じゃないんですから……って\n怪我でもしてたら大変ですし、早く助けないと！",
      "startTime": 119.7333180743,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_ball-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7466.666666699993,
          "startTime": 127.199984741
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7466.666666699993,
          "startTime": 127.199984741
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7466.666666699993,
          "startTime": 127.199984741
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "おーい、プール際を慌てて走ると危ないぞ～\n……あ、{user}がまたプールに落ちた",
      "startTime": 127.999984741,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9366.658528599984,
          "startTime": 137.3666432696
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、次のカット撮るよー！！\nえーと、プールをしゃぼん玉で埋め尽くすカットね",
      "startTime": 137.299976603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、バブルマシンって意外にしょぼいな\nこれってもっと出力上がらないの？　これで精一杯？",
      "startTime": 146.2999816892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "うー……しょうがない、kanaもやるわ\nそっちの貸して。うんそれ、吹いてシャボン玉出すやつ",
      "startTime": 156.4333099363,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6033.3236696000085,
          "startTime": 162.4666336059
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan018.m4a",
      "text": "ほらほらー！！　シャボン玉をぶわーっと……\nライトで照らして、思った通り！　きれーーい！！",
      "startTime": 167.2333099363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan019.m4a",
      "text": "もっと吹いて、シャボン玉で一杯にしないと……\n吹き続けないと、どんどん消えちゃうし",
      "startTime": 176.7666432696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさん、泡まみれになってますけど……",
      "startTime": 179.8666286784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan020.m4a",
      "text": "も～、それだけ頑張ってるってこと！\nあーでも吹きすぎて酸欠になってきた……",
      "startTime": 186.933300781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_03-kan021.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、倒れてる場合じゃないわ\nサビのとこ、一番kanaが目立つカットなんだから",
      "startTime": 193.5332997637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
